46
00:03:00,959 --> 00:03:05,279
The good thing about septic tanks is that
they are passive and do not require

47
00:03:05,279 --> 00:03:07,779
electrical energy to function.

48
00:03:07,779 --> 00:03:10,560
This makes this technology quite robust.

49
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:14,719
Construction is relatively costly but the
technology has a long service life

50
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:17,090
and requires little maintenance.

51
00:03:17,090 --> 00:03:22,029
The costs for mechanical emptying, however,
may be considerable.

52
